[{"id":"VR804128","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular circuit diagram in two scenarios, labeled Scenario 1 and Scenario 2. The circuit consists of a battery, two switches, and two lightbulbs. The left vertical branch has the battery. From top to bottom, the middle vertical branch has a switch and Bulb X. The right vertical branch has Bulb Y. The top horizontal branch has a switch between the left and middle vertical branches. Scenario 1 shows both switches are closed. Scenario 2 shows the switch on the top horizontal branch is closed while the switch on the middle vertical branch is open.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR804128.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two lightbulbs, Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> and Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi></math></span></span>, are in a circuit that also has a battery and two switches, as shown in the figures. For each scenario, which bulb or bulbs have current in them?</p><div class=\"table_wrapper\"><table class=\"tgroup align:center cols:3 colsep:0 frame:none rowsep:0\"><col class=\"colspec colname:col1 colnum:1 colsep:1\"/><thead class=\"thead\"><tr class=\"row rowsep:1\"><th class=\"entry colname:col1\"></th><th class=\"entry colname:col2\">Scenario <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></th><th class=\"entry colname:col3\">Scenario <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">A</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Current in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> only</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Current in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi></math></span></span> only</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">B</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Current in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> only</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Current in both bulbs</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">C</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Current in both bulbs</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Current in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi></math></span></span> only</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Current in both bulbs</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Current in both bulbs</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR804128_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">A</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">B</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">C</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">D</p>"],"answer":2}]